WEBVTT

00:02.609 --> 00:08.227
- ♪ (dramatic music) ♪
- (jeering)

00:08.233 --> 00:09.683
- INMATE: Yeah!
- (strangled) No!

00:11.050 --> 00:12.545
Drop it!

00:12.551 --> 00:13.782
- (knife clatters)
- (Miles grunts)

00:13.788 --> 00:15.162
(Vera grunting with effort)

00:16.071 --> 00:18.155
I want to be moved into
protection immediately.

00:18.161 --> 00:19.361
I don't think so.

00:19.367 --> 00:20.961
I want her in H Block by lunchtime.

00:20.967 --> 00:23.350
- You were his girlfriend?!
- He was obsessed with you...

00:23.356 --> 00:25.738
he even had a shrine to
you all over the wall.

00:25.744 --> 00:28.047
I have done some messed up shit.

00:28.053 --> 00:29.748
I swear, I do love you.

00:29.754 --> 00:33.217
You are the single biggest
mistake I have ever made.

00:33.223 --> 00:34.822
You are not a man, you are a puppet

00:34.828 --> 00:37.920
with Ferguson's hand so far up your
arse you will never be free of her.

00:37.926 --> 00:40.402
Now, I'm gonna get out and
you're gonna come with me.

00:40.408 --> 00:44.642
♪ (dramatic rhythmic drum beats) ♪

00:45.291 --> 00:46.526
(hushed) Get me out of here!

00:46.532 --> 00:48.315
I'm not a miracle worker.

00:48.321 --> 00:49.615
You find a way.

00:49.621 --> 00:51.932
While she's still breathing
she is never gonna stop.

00:51.938 --> 00:55.149
To get justice, sometimes
you'll need to cross a line.

00:55.155 --> 00:56.355
♪ (dramatic drum beat) ♪

00:56.909 --> 00:58.983
- (retching)
- (cutlery clatters)

00:58.989 --> 01:01.800
VERA: All right, everyone step back!
Step back. All right, give her air.

01:01.801 --> 01:04.102
- But we can't go back.
- We have to, there'll be a count.

01:04.102 --> 01:06.418
- Shit! Okay, just go, I'll be right behind you.
- Come on.

01:07.345 --> 01:09.571
Oi, Novak, stop right there!

01:09.956 --> 01:11.765
I think I've discovered an escape plan.

01:12.288 --> 01:14.479
Soon as lockdown's lifted we gotta move.

01:17.983 --> 01:19.515
(scraping and sighing)

01:19.521 --> 01:21.411
(Allie reading aloud)
<i>I'm sorry but I had to lie to you.</i>

01:21.417 --> 01:22.783
<i>But I think I found a way</i>

01:22.789 --> 01:24.507
- <i>to protect you...</i>
- (hushed) Oh, shit!

01:24.513 --> 01:25.713
<i>to get you out.</i>

01:25.818 --> 01:29.144
<i>So, get going. Run like
hell and clear your name.</i>

01:29.263 --> 01:31.052
<i>I need to do something else.</i>

01:32.125 --> 01:33.450
<i>I made a deal...</i>

01:33.953 --> 01:35.830
<i>to share my escape plan.</i>

01:36.364 --> 01:37.564
(digging)

01:37.782 --> 01:39.321
- (soil falling)
- No!

01:39.929 --> 01:41.870
Let me out of here!

01:41.921 --> 01:44.921
♪♪

01:48.107 --> 01:50.819
No!

01:53.910 --> 01:56.812
(footsteps echoing)

01:56.818 --> 01:58.170
<i>♪ (theme music) ♪</i>

01:58.176 --> 02:03.898
