♪ (rhythmic drum beats) ♪

11:09.497 --> 11:13.198
(muffled train clattering)

11:14.513 --> 11:17.513
♪ (music mellows) ♪

11:20.261 --> 11:22.198
- _
- ♪ (echoing drum beat) ♪

11:22.671 --> 11:25.085
♪ (music gradually intensifies) ♪

11:25.091 --> 11:26.291
♪ (echoing drum beat) ♪

11:28.152 --> 11:29.352
_

11:29.358 --> 11:31.054
- ♪ (echoing drum beat) ♪
- (hushed) Fuck!

11:31.371 --> 11:32.571
(exhales quietly)

11:49.652 --> 11:51.838
(phones ringing)

11:52.549 --> 11:53.846
How'd it go with the police?

11:53.852 --> 11:56.450
- They got any leads?
- Why the hell are you still here?

11:57.050 --> 11:58.870
Uh, I wanna make things right.

11:59.041 --> 12:01.219
If you want the Deputyship
back, you can forget it.

12:01.225 --> 12:03.154
If it was up to me, you'd be
queueing at the job centre.

12:03.160 --> 12:05.144
I wanna make things right with <i>us</i>.

12:05.425 --> 12:07.211
(phones continue ringing in background)

12:07.217 --> 12:08.739
(hushed) Are you that deluded?

12:09.843 --> 12:11.059
(hushed) I love you.

12:12.677 --> 12:14.554
Just give me a chance to prove it.

12:14.560 --> 12:18.468
I will prove that you helped
Ferguson escape, and when I do,

12:18.474 --> 12:21.137
that evidence you think
you have on me is hearsay.

12:21.325 --> 12:22.755
Be my word against yours.

12:22.761 --> 12:23.961
(door beeps unlocked)

12:24.536 --> 12:26.185
- (phone continues ringing)
- (door slams)

12:26.191 --> 12:27.714
Okay, come through. But make it quick,

12:27.720 --> 12:29.930
I've got a call with the
board in five minutes.

12:30.308 --> 12:31.520
- It's the lockdown.
- (Vera sighs exasperatedly)

12:31.526 --> 12:34.457
The women are going crazy, they
are this close to losing it.

12:34.463 --> 12:36.735
Most of them have never been
near the workshop and they don't

12:36.741 --> 12:39.126
understand why they're being
punished for someone else's breakout.

12:39.132 --> 12:41.439
We've already established
Jenkins distracted an officer,

12:41.445 --> 12:42.851
maybe others were involved too.

12:42.857 --> 12:45.556
The escape worked because
no one knew about it.

12:45.562 --> 12:48.689
They're being denied their basic
rights here. They need fresh air,

12:48.695 --> 12:52.063
they need to eat together, they
need TVs on, they need to work.

12:54.070 --> 12:55.270
(sighs)

12:55.276 --> 12:57.108
The women respect you, Ms Bennett,

12:57.229 --> 13:00.405
but if you leave them cooped up for
much longer you're gonna lose them.

13:01.026 --> 13:02.226
Wait outside please.

13:03.405 --> 13:05.234
(phones continue
ringing in background)

13:05.717 --> 13:07.132
(Vera sighs deeply)

13:07.138 --> 13:08.982
- (door closes)
- What do you think?

13:08.988 --> 13:11.035
Well, J Block are still going nuts.

13:11.041 --> 13:12.576
Now D Block are kicking off,

13:12.582 --> 13:14.367
and... and we've moved people around.

13:14.755 --> 13:17.149
- (mobile phone ringing as well)
- I mean, it... it could be a good circuit breaker.

13:17.155 --> 13:18.490
Just get things settled?

13:19.158 --> 13:21.275
- (desk phone rings)
- (Vera sighs deeply)

13:21.281 --> 13:23.657
Right, I'll lift the
lockdown, you implement it...

13:23.658 --> 13:26.478
- but TV privileges stay suspended.
- Sure.

13:27.259 --> 13:28.459
- Yes!
- ASSISTANT: Mr Burton...

13:28.465 --> 13:30.887
- KAZ: Thanks for helping.
- WILL: Well, it works for me.

13:30.997 --> 13:32.605
Last thing I need is a riot.

13:32.898 --> 13:34.187
Late nights?

13:34.422 --> 13:35.708
You look like crap.

13:35.997 --> 13:37.669
Uh... knackered.

13:37.675 --> 13:40.452
Double shifts. Cops in and
out, interviewing everyone.

13:40.622 --> 13:42.017
They got any leads?

13:42.200 --> 13:43.400
I don't think so.

13:43.406 --> 13:46.325
I don't get it. Why would
Franky leave with Ferguson?

13:46.331 --> 13:48.318
Where would they go? It doesn't add up.

13:48.434 --> 13:49.634
♪ (echoing drum beat) ♪

13:51.317 --> 13:53.753
Sooner or later they'll find Ferguson...

13:54.186 --> 13:55.386
♪ (echoing drum beat) ♪

13:56.984 --> 13:58.468
and she'll be back.

13:58.474 --> 14:04.996
♪ (rhythmic drumming) ♪

14:05.002 --> 14:06.202
_

14:10.485 --> 14:11.685
Hey.

14:12.973 --> 14:15.209
Jesus, mate, you look shithouse.

14:17.073 --> 14:18.485
Vera's gunning for me.

14:18.556 --> 14:20.296
She thinks I helped Ferguson.

14:20.302 --> 14:22.038
So put her off the scent.

14:22.303 --> 14:23.503
How?

14:24.319 --> 14:26.537
I dunno, use that
fucked up brain of yours.

14:26.543 --> 14:28.155
Mate, this is your problem too.

14:30.663 --> 14:32.451
- I've done my bit, okay?
- (Jake grimaces)

14:32.580 --> 14:34.560
And I feel sick about it.

14:34.566 --> 14:37.888
But I did it for Vera
and the women, all right?

14:37.894 --> 14:40.895
You are not my responsibility,
you're on your own. You got that?

14:41.274 --> 14:42.474
You got that?!

14:42.480 --> 14:43.680
(breathing heavily)

14:43.686 --> 14:44.886
Mmm.

14:47.270 --> 14:48.764
(exhales heavily)

14:49.552 --> 14:50.752
- (sighs)
- (door slams)

14:52.052 --> 14:53.747
(P.A. announcement)
<i>Lockdown is now lifted.</i>

14:53.753 --> 14:56.193
- <i>I repeat. Lockdown...</i>
- (door beep unlocked, inmates cheer)

14:57.676 --> 14:59.699
Ah, I want some air!

14:59.705 --> 15:04.058
- BOOMER: Halle-fuckin'-lujah
- INMATE: Woohoo!

15:04.064 --> 15:05.330
KAZ: Want some air?

15:05.473 --> 15:06.673
You comin'?

15:06.679 --> 15:09.006
- INMATE: Yeah!
- Woo! About time.

15:10.501 --> 15:12.908
(inmates cheering and clapping)

15:14.290 --> 15:17.017
Ah, fuck, the air's great!

15:17.166 --> 15:19.779
- Yes!
- Oh, you're the best, Kaz.

15:19.885 --> 15:21.413
Onya, Kaz.

15:21.419 --> 15:23.182
- Cheers, Kaz.
- You bloody legend!

15:23.183 --> 15:25.272
- Kaz!
- Onya, Kaz.

15:25.278 --> 15:27.697
You're welcome. Nice to see ya.

15:27.703 --> 15:30.623
(general chatter)

15:30.984 --> 15:34.715
Hey, M-M-Miss College, is
there any news on Sonia Stevens?

15:34.721 --> 15:36.301
- Nah.
- Like anything?

15:36.307 --> 15:38.432
- As far as I know she's still critical, Jenkins.
- Oh, just...

15:38.438 --> 15:40.318
- like, tell me something.
- Sorry, love.

15:44.900 --> 15:46.100
Hey.

15:46.440 --> 15:48.071
What the hell are you doin' here?

15:48.570 --> 15:49.892
Just wanna talk.

15:49.898 --> 15:51.617
I never wanna talk to you again.

15:52.102 --> 15:54.296
- It's better if nobody knows about us.
- (scoffs)

15:55.984 --> 15:57.703
They ain't gonna hear it from me.

15:59.788 --> 16:01.474
INMATE: Oi, Wanda!

16:01.584 --> 16:03.260
- KAZ: Hey.
- LIZ: Hey.

16:05.092 --> 16:07.097
You two know what Franky was up to?

16:07.490 --> 16:09.371
No, not a clue.

16:10.010 --> 16:12.825
Franky takes Ferguson with her...

16:14.207 --> 16:16.108
how the fuck does that work?

16:16.293 --> 16:17.493
Dunno.

16:17.611 --> 16:19.415
Maybe she didn't have a choice?

16:27.298 --> 16:28.498
Hey...

16:30.204 --> 16:32.181
Franky gave me this before she left.

16:32.189 --> 16:34.709
I've been hangin' onto it and
lookin' at it, thinkin' about her.

16:34.849 --> 16:36.790
(sighs)

16:36.882 --> 16:38.769
Where do you reckon she is right now?

16:39.782 --> 16:41.584
- Bermuda...
- (chuckles)

16:41.590 --> 16:43.390
- Barbados...
- ♪ (gentle music) ♪

16:43.467 --> 16:45.379
- Broadmeadows? (chuckles)
- (chuckles)

16:47.066 --> 16:48.924
Nah, she's got a job to do.

16:49.397 --> 16:51.823
She won't be going
anywhere until it's done.

17:00.213 --> 17:02.954
(breathing heavily)

17:02.960 --> 17:05.147
(news report) <i>Doyle has been
charged with the shooting murder</i>

17:05.154 --> 17:07.425
<i>of TV personality, Mike Pennisi,</i>

17:07.542 --> 17:10.425
<i>while Ms Ferguson was
serving time for the murder</i>

17:10.432 --> 17:12.541
<i>of former inmate, Bea Smith</i>

17:12.627 --> 17:15.770
<i>Serious questions are being
asked about security measures</i>

17:15.776 --> 17:17.762
<i>at Wentworth Correctional Centre</i>

17:17.768 --> 17:22.270
<i>following a number of high profile
incidents over recent years.</i>

17:22.276 --> 17:24.856
<i>Conservative lobbyists are
calling on the Government</i>

17:24.862 --> 17:28.377
<i>to implement tougher
restrictions on prisoners...</i>

17:30.044 --> 17:31.244
(hushed) Jesus!

17:31.250 --> 17:32.872
Gidge, what the fuck happened?

17:32.878 --> 17:34.728
- Has anyone seen you?
- (incredulously) No.

17:34.734 --> 17:35.950
BRIDGET: (whispered) Oh, fuck!

17:35.956 --> 17:38.849
- Oi, what's this?
- It's nothing, I... I was rushing...

17:38.855 --> 17:40.841
Franky, what the hell were you thinking?

17:40.847 --> 17:42.937
Look, I gotta keep movin'. I
was gonna ask you for a ride,

17:42.943 --> 17:43.950
- but...
- To where?!

17:43.951 --> 17:47.460
- Iman's place.
- Oh, Franky, this is crazy!

17:47.891 --> 17:49.091
We've been over this.

17:49.097 --> 17:52.090
If the police... if there was any
evidence, they would have found it!

17:52.096 --> 17:54.306
She's not a suspect, it's just me.

17:54.312 --> 17:56.494
Now, I'm gonna go down for
murder if I don't do something.

17:56.500 --> 17:58.602
We are gonna get another lawyer.
Okay, this is not the way...

17:58.608 --> 18:01.804
- It's not gonna make a difference! I need evidence!
- I'm gonna remortgage the house...

18:01.810 --> 18:04.356
And I'm not gonna find it
sitting in a prison cell.

18:05.010 --> 18:06.802
I wish you'd told me
you were planning this.

18:06.808 --> 18:08.395
You would have talked me out of it.

18:09.692 --> 18:11.699
(sighs)

18:11.997 --> 18:14.377
- Where's Ferguson?
- I dunno, I never saw her.

18:14.383 --> 18:15.583
Baby, where are you sleeping?

18:15.589 --> 18:17.562
- It doesn't matter.
- Is is safe?

18:17.563 --> 18:18.683
- That...
- Is it... is it...

18:18.750 --> 18:20.557
COLLINS: Ms Westfall, it's the police.

18:20.665 --> 18:22.665
(indistinct news report
continues in background)

18:22.671 --> 18:25.671
♪ (gentle music) ♪

18:30.873 --> 18:32.073
(door opens)

18:32.079 --> 18:33.279
Yeah, hi.

18:33.285 --> 18:35.418
I'm Detective Collins,
this is Detective Hydari,

18:35.419 --> 18:36.967
can we come in, please?

18:37.344 --> 18:38.544
Why?

18:38.550 --> 18:41.538
COLLINS: We have some questions
about the nature of your relationship

18:41.544 --> 18:42.950
with Francesca Doyle.

18:43.657 --> 18:45.460
Oh, I can answer questions here.

18:45.466 --> 18:47.165
We'd also like a look around.

18:47.269 --> 18:48.469
Why's that?

18:48.475 --> 18:51.185
We know you visited Doyle
a number of times recently.

18:51.191 --> 18:54.598
- You care to explain why?
- Because she needed psychological support.

18:55.121 --> 18:58.550
Well, none of you other ex-clients
needed to see you, why did she?

18:58.556 --> 19:00.847
Well, I can't discuss
her personal situation.

19:00.853 --> 19:02.535
(scoffs) We're hunting
an escaped criminal,

19:02.541 --> 19:04.542
we don't have time for
confidentiality bullshit.

19:04.548 --> 19:06.886
COLLINS: It really would be better if
you could just let us in, Ms Westfall.

19:06.892 --> 19:09.010
HYDARI: Otherwise we might think
you've got something to hide.

19:09.016 --> 19:10.944
- BRIDGET: Do you have a search warrant?
- We could get one.

19:10.950 --> 19:12.884
- Oh, good, then you can get one.
- Ms Westfall...

19:12.890 --> 19:16.101
Look, I'm sorry, I'm not gonna stand
here and be spoken to like this,

19:16.107 --> 19:17.457
I need to rest.

19:17.640 --> 19:21.260
So, if you feel you need to
search my house then get a warrant,

19:21.266 --> 19:23.433
otherwise, don't waste my time.

19:31.222 --> 19:32.422
(sighs exasperatedly)

19:32.612 --> 19:34.128
(hushed) Franky...

19:36.202 --> 19:38.534
Oh, for fuck's sake!

19:39.198 --> 19:41.423
- (sighs deeply)
- You were close with Doyle...

19:42.082 --> 19:44.386
I think you knew
what she was planning.

19:44.392 --> 19:47.261
- Now, I'm not expecting you to lag...
- (phones persistently ringing in background)

19:47.285 --> 19:49.001
that is not why you're here...

19:49.007 --> 19:53.788
I have reason to believe
an officer was involved.

19:55.983 --> 19:57.415
What can you tell me about that?

20:00.313 --> 20:02.501
You've protected an officer
before over contraband,

20:02.507 --> 20:05.598
did the same officer help
Doyle and Ferguson escape?

20:07.246 --> 20:08.446
Novak...

20:10.214 --> 20:13.226
this is a very serious
situation. If you help me...

20:13.684 --> 20:15.286
I will advocate on your behalf.

20:15.292 --> 20:17.208
I will see if I can get
your sentence reduced.

20:17.214 --> 20:18.598
(hushed) Just tell me what you know.

20:18.622 --> 20:22.843
(phones continue ringing in background)

20:23.115 --> 20:24.604
I don't know anything.

20:25.677 --> 20:27.279
(mobile phone ringing)

20:28.201 --> 20:30.852
(P.A. announcement) <i>Attention, compound.
Attention, compound.</i>

20:30.858 --> 20:33.091
<i>All women to report to
assigned work duties.</i>

20:33.097 --> 20:34.297
Novak!

20:35.475 --> 20:38.444
(hushed) Where have you been?!
I've been looking for you.

20:41.949 --> 20:43.218
What'd the Governor want?

20:44.620 --> 20:47.452
She thinks an officer was
involved in the escape.

20:47.458 --> 20:48.658
What'd you tell her?

20:48.781 --> 20:49.981
Nothing!

20:50.205 --> 20:51.866
(sighs) Okay, good.

20:52.002 --> 20:53.202
- Wait!
- Oi.

20:54.783 --> 20:56.420
I wanna know what happened.

20:57.783 --> 21:03.389
I need to know that that...
<i>bitch</i> is gone for good.

21:03.395 --> 21:04.667
The job's done.

21:05.155 --> 21:06.593
You just need to keep quiet.

21:06.749 --> 21:08.059
I want details.

21:08.380 --> 21:09.858
D-d-did she suffer?

21:10.578 --> 21:11.778
What?!

21:11.784 --> 21:13.605
I wanna know that she suffered.

21:13.611 --> 21:17.385
I wanna hear about every
last fucking scream.

21:17.391 --> 21:18.892
This conversation's over.

21:18.986 --> 21:22.004
Ferguson's dead, okay. End of.

21:22.010 --> 21:25.010
♪ (muffled dance music intensifies) ♪

21:33.825 --> 21:35.025
(exhales quietly)

21:36.325 --> 21:41.245
- (extended whooshing flourish)
- _

21:41.251 --> 21:42.511
Oh, Miss Miles...

21:42.790 --> 21:45.623
Miss Miles, still haven't
heard nuffin' about Sonia, like.

21:45.629 --> 21:47.322
Can you... can you find out for us?

21:47.328 --> 21:48.630
- Sit down, Jenkins.
- No! Just...

21:48.636 --> 21:51.083
- fuckin' tell me somethin'. Sit down.
- Sit down!

21:51.560 --> 21:54.470
Sit... I'll fuckin' sit... sit down.

21:56.791 --> 21:59.182
Hey, Sonia wouldn't be
dead or nuffin' would she?

21:59.188 --> 22:00.909
Like, 'cause they'd have
to say, wouldn't they?

22:00.915 --> 22:02.408
- Yeah, of course they would.
- Yeah.

22:04.090 --> 22:05.520
You don't look very worried.

22:05.918 --> 22:07.410
Just eat your lunch, love.

22:07.416 --> 22:08.616
I'm not hungry.

22:10.418 --> 22:13.035
All right, I'm missin'
Franky too, all right.

22:13.041 --> 22:15.658
Well, maybe she could
come visit in disguise.

22:15.664 --> 22:21.197
(inmates cheer and clap)

22:21.257 --> 22:22.463
BOOMER: Hey, Juice...

22:22.469 --> 22:25.019
how was hospital?! They
glue your tongue back on?

22:25.025 --> 22:26.225
(inmates laugh)

22:26.231 --> 22:27.431
Sorry, what?

22:27.437 --> 22:29.089
Was that... was that like sign language?

22:29.095 --> 22:30.894
'Cause I can speak that, yeah.

22:31.613 --> 22:34.911
(inmates laugh)

22:35.180 --> 22:37.596
- (sighs loudly)
- Hey, sugar tits.

22:37.699 --> 22:40.514
Yeah, that's me, sweet and sour.

22:41.166 --> 22:43.307
So, um, what's J Block like?

22:43.636 --> 22:47.034
Oh, it's deadly. We plait each
other's hair and have all night orgies.

22:47.040 --> 22:49.343
Oh, yeah? We have orgies too.

22:49.746 --> 22:51.612
Liz goes <i>off</i>.

22:54.054 --> 22:55.448
How'd ya sleep?

22:55.515 --> 22:56.715
Like shit.

22:56.721 --> 22:59.422
That's what happens when you
burn your mattress, you dumb arse.

22:59.428 --> 23:01.194
You want a <i>fuckin'</i>
fist in your mouth?

23:01.200 --> 23:04.105
I got a big mouth, you wouldn't
even touch the sides, mate.

23:04.111 --> 23:05.311
(Sharon chuckles)

23:05.651 --> 23:09.379
This chick here... my fuckin'
property, you got that?

23:09.385 --> 23:10.585
Whatever.

23:10.847 --> 23:12.047
Leave her alone.

23:13.245 --> 23:15.915
- Why are you protecting her, you fuckin' her?
- Don't be stupid.

23:15.921 --> 23:18.732
Look at my girlfriend
again... I'll cut ya throat.

23:18.899 --> 23:20.838
Here's a news flash, babe,

23:20.844 --> 23:23.438
I'm not interested in you
or your drug fucked mum!

23:23.871 --> 23:25.477
Hey, fuckin' cunt!

23:25.483 --> 23:26.879
- KAZ: Oi! Oi!
- SPIKE: Come here!

23:26.885 --> 23:29.479
Cool it. We're good. We're good.

23:30.059 --> 23:31.844
I don't care how you
did things in J Block.

23:31.850 --> 23:34.757
When you're with us you show each
other some respect. You got it?

23:34.852 --> 23:36.052
I'm comin' for ya, dog.

23:36.058 --> 23:38.858
You touch her, you answer to me. Now
get your food or get the fuck out.

23:44.104 --> 23:45.304
Sit down.

23:46.174 --> 23:48.676
(solitary clapping)

23:49.276 --> 23:50.476
You right?

23:51.995 --> 23:53.907
(door beeps unlocked)

23:55.735 --> 23:58.735
♪ (rhythmic music intensifies) ♪

24:05.587 --> 24:08.165
♪ (warped pulsating rhythm) ♪

24:08.171 --> 24:09.371
Fuck off!

24:13.595 --> 24:16.595
♪ (quietly tense music) ♪

24:21.491 --> 24:24.099
- What the fuck are you doin'?
- Ah, just lookin' for someone.

24:24.409 --> 24:25.609
Who?

24:26.719 --> 24:29.214
That young Koori girl. They
said she was in this unit.

24:29.220 --> 24:30.420
Spike send ya?

24:30.426 --> 24:32.909
- Nah.
- Oh, yeah, so what do ya want her for?

24:32.915 --> 24:36.121
Newbie. (laughs nervously) Connected
with the mob. It's what we do.

24:36.127 --> 24:37.715
Oh, yeah, right. Well...

24:37.721 --> 24:40.440
not sneakin' round other
people's cells is what we do.

24:40.446 --> 24:41.833
- Okay?
- Got it. (chuckles)

24:41.903 --> 24:44.924
Couldn't give a rat's arse
about your girlfriend, Spike.

24:45.434 --> 24:47.362
You think you're so fuckin' funny?!

24:47.770 --> 24:51.395
- With your wisecracks and your smart-arsed comments.
- (scoffs and chuckles)

24:51.481 --> 24:53.674
Mints aren't cuttin' it for ya, mate.

24:55.270 --> 24:57.301
Monte Carlos? Love 'em.

24:57.307 --> 24:59.008
- Yeah, nearly out.
- You know if you split 'em

24:59.014 --> 25:01.085
it's kinda like you
get twice the amount.

25:01.686 --> 25:04.686
♪♪

25:05.577 --> 25:07.686
- Piss off, Spike.
- Nah.

25:08.460 --> 25:10.174
Nah, I don't think so.

25:11.514 --> 25:12.714
Don't do this.

25:12.890 --> 25:15.402
Not so fuckin' funny
anymore, are ya?

25:15.585 --> 25:16.785
LIZ: Hello, hello.

25:17.210 --> 25:18.410
Who's this?

25:18.484 --> 25:20.921
- Rita... Connors
- Liz and Allie.

25:20.927 --> 25:22.424
She lookin' for the black chick.

25:22.430 --> 25:24.917
- Oh, Ruby?
- I think she's in the showers.

25:25.111 --> 25:26.697
Great, thanks.

25:27.595 --> 25:29.790
- Fuck me, it works!
- Hey?

25:31.517 --> 25:32.717
Thanks.

25:32.977 --> 25:35.101
♪ (rhythmic music intensifying) ♪

25:35.180 --> 25:37.113
MILES: Hey, this isn't a race track!

25:42.926 --> 25:44.613
- (breathing heavily)
- ♪ (music quells) ♪

25:49.121 --> 25:51.425
(breathing heavily)

25:54.010 --> 25:55.210
Oh, shit!

25:55.833 --> 25:57.112
(door closes)

26:02.416 --> 26:03.741
She's breathing.

26:07.852 --> 26:09.078
Sit on the bed.

26:11.266 --> 26:12.466
(water running)

26:12.472 --> 26:14.282
Why the hell did you do that?

26:14.288 --> 26:15.664
(sighs) I dunno.

26:15.670 --> 26:17.992
- What do you mean "you don't know"?
- I can't remember.

26:17.998 --> 26:20.459
- What the fuck's that supposed to mean.
- (sighs)

26:21.147 --> 26:23.083
I think my hand's broken.

26:24.145 --> 26:25.345
Gimme a look.

26:25.652 --> 26:27.237
Knuckle's dislocated.

26:27.450 --> 26:29.573
Look at me. Wiggle your toes.

26:29.579 --> 26:30.908
- Why? Ow!
- (bones crunch)

26:30.914 --> 26:33.926
- Fuck! (grimaces)
- Shhh. Sh-sh-sh-sh-sh.

26:33.932 --> 26:35.132
(breathing through the pain)

26:35.409 --> 26:38.416
Shhh. Shhh.

26:38.422 --> 26:40.026
(exhales deeply)

26:40.032 --> 26:41.670
Need to get some ice on that.

26:42.939 --> 26:44.433
I don't need ya help.

26:48.034 --> 26:49.771
(sighs)

26:51.893 --> 26:53.093
(inhales deeply)

26:53.099 --> 26:55.366
They find out it was
you, they'll charge ya.

26:55.372 --> 26:58.373
That nine month stretch of yours
will turn into bloody years.

26:58.379 --> 27:00.293
They say you're called "Connors" now.

27:00.764 --> 27:02.186
(sighs)

27:02.192 --> 27:03.595
Rita Connors.

27:04.640 --> 27:06.429
Lots of things have changed.

27:07.050 --> 27:08.366
So, what ya in for?

27:09.756 --> 27:11.029
Armed robbery.

27:11.035 --> 27:12.235
(scoffs)

27:12.241 --> 27:14.241
- What, so you're a bikie now?
- (chuckles quietly)

27:14.724 --> 27:15.924
Yeah.

27:17.687 --> 27:20.095
I made some pretty dumb choices.

27:20.983 --> 27:22.825
Done a lot of things I regret.

27:24.688 --> 27:26.461
- (siren wails and P.A. announcement blares)
- <i>Attention, compound. Attention, compound.</i>

27:26.467 --> 27:28.243
- They found her.
- Oh, fuck!

27:28.249 --> 27:30.882
I'm rostered on in the laundry.
They're gonna see my hands, Rita.

27:31.046 --> 27:33.585
- <i>Code Purple in the shower block.</i>
- (grimaces)

27:33.591 --> 27:35.351
- (siren continues wailing)
- Stretch it out.

27:36.048 --> 27:37.853
Don't say a word to anyone, okay?

27:38.063 --> 27:39.263
Okay.

27:40.126 --> 27:41.326
Go.

27:41.759 --> 27:43.139
Fuck off!

27:44.390 --> 27:45.590
(sighs)

27:45.741 --> 27:48.148
GUARD: Out of the way.
Nothing to see here.

27:48.282 --> 27:50.554
- Coming through, coming through.
- INMATE: Fuck!

27:51.044 --> 27:52.561
- GUARD: Out of the way.
- Who did that?

27:52.567 --> 27:55.074
MILES: You tell me. Better
still, tell the Governor.

27:55.080 --> 27:56.280
KAZ: (hushed) Fucking animals!

27:56.801 --> 27:58.001
Oi!

27:58.177 --> 27:59.989
You know anything about that?

28:00.297 --> 28:01.497
(chuckling) Nuh.

28:01.989 --> 28:03.591
Don't you bullshit to me.

28:03.597 --> 28:05.580
I couldn't give a shit
about the crazy bitch.

28:06.968 --> 28:09.968
♪ (tense rhythmic music intensifies) ♪

28:21.147 --> 28:22.347
Argh!

28:22.353 --> 28:24.012
(car revs, tyres squeal)

28:24.018 --> 28:25.218
Fuck!

28:25.224 --> 28:26.960
- (groans and exhales)
- (hushed through clenched teeth) Fuck!

28:26.966 --> 28:28.362
(grimaces and groans) Mmm.

28:28.462 --> 28:31.462
- ♪♪
- (sighs and breaths through the pain)

28:35.661 --> 28:37.392
- Ooh!
